You now need `backend/.env` to include:

```text
ZERODHA_API_KEY=...
ZERODHA_API_SECRET=...
```

Also set your Kite developer console redirect URL to:

```text
http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/auth/kite/callback
```

Then start backend and frontend. If the token is missing/expired, click “Sign in with Kite”; the backend will save the daily token automatically.

